			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>&gt; I wanted to use vanilla http and not have the overhead of launching a browser and was frustrated that Capybara didn’t have a driver to suit my needs.</p>
<p>Hopes this helps you&#8230;.</p>
<p>Akephalos[0]: &#8220;Akephalos is a full-stack headless browser for integration testing with Capybara. It is built on top of HtmlUnit, a GUI-less browser for the Java platform, but can be run on both JRuby and MRI with no need for JRuby to be installed on the system.&#8221;</p>
